## File Structure

pilgrimage-website/
|-- backend/
| |-- server.js
|-- frontend/
| |-- index.html
| |-- styles.css
| |-- app.js
|-- README.md

Open your web browser and navigate to http://localhost:3000 to view the application.

Features
Display upcoming events on the webpage.
User-friendly interface with responsive design.
Click on an event to view more detailed information.
Navigate back to the list of events.
Technologies Used
Backend: Node.js, Express
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Contributing
If you'd like to contribute, please fork the repository and create a pull request. Feel free to open an issue if you have any suggestions or find any issues.

